headline: Patrick Higgins Named Chief Revenue Officer at Robots & Pencils
summary: Robots & Pencils, an AI-first, global digital innovation firm specializing in cloud-native web, mobile, and app modernization, today announced the appointment of Patrick Higgins as Chief Revenue Officer (CRO). A seasoned technology leader with over 15 years of experience driving digital innovation for Fortune 500 companies, Higgins steps into a pivotal role to deepen client partnerships, scale impact, and fuel the company's next phase of growth.
